if it were a unanimous decision.

260
00:21:43,402 --> 00:21:47,739
Don't worry, even if we lose.
We can always lodge an appeal.

261
00:21:50,342 --> 00:21:52,711
I wanted to tell you this
before the ruling.

262
00:21:52,911 --> 00:21:54,513
