400
00:36:47,271 --> 00:36:49,373
-Are you buying a new phone?
-Yes.

401
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:51,275
Is there anything you'd prefer?

402
00:36:54,412 --> 00:36:55,746
I'll have this one.

